## Rollback Procedure

### Automated Rollback Triggers

| Signal | Threshold | Action |
|--------|-----------|--------|
| Error rate increase | > 2x baseline | Automatic rollback |
| Latency P99 increase | > 50% baseline | Alert + manual rollback |
| Prediction distribution shift | KS statistic > 0.1 | Alert + investigate |

### Manual Rollback Steps

1. Identify the previous production version in the registry
2. Update the production alias to point to the previous version
3. Verify serving infrastructure picks up the change
4. Monitor metrics for 15 minutes after rollback
5. Document the rollback reason and root cause

